                    Depending on the processing field the stored value is updated as follows: if processing is 'ADD',
                    then the currently received value is added to the stored value, if processing is 'LAST',
                    then the currently received value overrides the stored value, if processing is 'MAX',
                    then the currently received value overrides the stored value only in case the stored value
                    is lower and if processing is 'COUNT' then the currently received value is ignored and
